data.description: Best and Final Offers Due 11/30@12PM  Nestled in the picturesque countryside of Allen Township, Northampton County, Pennsylvania, this charming residence offers a perfect blend of rustic tranquility and modern comfort.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting floor plan, flooded with an abundance of natural light. The interior features a blend of timeless elements and contemporary finishes, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. Hardwood floors flow throughout the main living areas, adding a touch of elegance to the space.  The spacious living room provides an ideal gathering spot for family and friends, featuring a cozy fireplace that serves as the focal point of the room. The adjacent kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, equipped with modern appliances,  granite countertops, built-in island, and beautiful cabinetry.  The master suite offers a private oasis, complete with a well-appointed en-suite bathroom and ample closet space. Additional bedrooms provide comfort and flexibility for family members or guests.   Outside, the property features a generously sized fenced-in backyard, providing ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply unwinding amidst the natural beauty. The patio and deck areas offers a perfect setting for dining or relaxing.  Located in Allen Township, residents enjoy the benefits of a peaceful, tight-knit community while still being within convenient reach of nearby amenities, schools, and recreational facilities.
